## üîß Environment Variables & Customization

### Base Configuration

| Variable                          | Description                                                           | Default                 |
| ----------------------------------|---------------------------------------------------------------------- | ----------------------- |
| `PUBLIC_FEATURE_PRIVATE_LINKS`    | Enable private access to your link shortener instance. `on` \| `off`  | `off`                   |
| `DATABASE_URL`                    | Connection string (SQLite, PostgreSQL, MySQL, Cloudflare D1)          | ‚Äì                       |
| `ORIGIN`                          | Base URL for your short-link domain                                   | ‚Äì                       |
| `MAIL_PROVIDER`                   | `smtp` \| `mailgun` \| `mailpit` (see below)                          | ‚Äì                       |
| `PUBLIC_TTL_TEMP`                 | Default expiry for anonymous/temporary links                          | `WEEK`                  |
| `PUBLIC_TTL_USER`                 | Default expiry for user-generated or authenticated short URLs         | `EVER`                  |

### Sending Emails

To login to your account or even create a new one, you need to setup a email provider.
Choose one of the following providers:

#### Mailpit

Set `MAIL_PROVIDER` to `MAILPIT`

| Variable            | Description                                                      | Default                 |
| ------------------- |----------------------------------------------------------------- | ----------------------- |
| `MAILPIT_DOMAIN`    | URL to your Mailpit Server  (e.g. `https://my.mailpit.io`)       | ‚Äî                       |
| `MAIL_FROM`         | Envelope ‚Äúfrom‚Äù address for outgoing mail                        | `noreply@example.com`   |

#### Mailgun

Set `MAIL_PROVIDER` to `MAILGUN`

| Variable            | Description                                                      | Default                 |
| ------------------- |----------------------------------------------------------------- | ----------------------- |
| `MAILGUN_DOMAIN`    | Domain of your Mailgun account  (e.g. `mg.example.com`)          | ‚Äî                       |
| `MAILGUN_API_KEY`   | API key for your Mailgun account                                 | ‚Äî                       |
| `MAILGUN_URL`       | URL of Mailgun ( e.g. `https://api.mailgun.net`)                 | ‚Äî                       |
| `MAIL_FROM`         | Envelope ‚Äúfrom‚Äù address for outgoing mail                        | `noreply@example.com`   |

#### SMTP

Set `MAIL_PROVIDER` to `SMTP`.

| Variable            | Description                                                      | Default                 |
| ------------------- |----------------------------------------------------------------- | ----------------------- |
| `MAIL_HOST`         | SMTP host for sending emails                                     | ‚Äî                       |
| `MAIL_PORT`         | SMTP port                                                        | ‚Äî                       |
| `MAIL_USER`         | SMTP username                                                    | ‚Äî                       |
| `MAIL_PASS`         | SMTP password                                                    | ‚Äî                       |
| `MAIL_FROM`         | Envelope ‚Äúfrom‚Äù address for outgoing mail                        | `noreply@example.com`   |

